specialist_training_land_tech = {
	allow = {
		or = {
			and = {
				specialist_training_land_tech = 1
				not = { specialist_training_land_tech = 2 }
			}
			and = {
				specialist_training_land_tech = 2
				not = { specialist_training_land_tech = 3 }
			}
			and = {
				specialist_training_land_tech = 3
				not = { specialist_training_land_tech = 4 }
			}
			and = {
				specialist_training_land_tech = 4
				not = { specialist_training_land_tech = 5 }
			}
			and = {
				specialist_training_land_tech = 5
				not = { specialist_training_land_tech = 6 }
			}
			and = {
				specialist_training_land_tech = 6
				not = { specialist_training_land_tech = 7 }
			}
			and = {
				specialist_training_land_tech = 7
				not = { specialist_training_land_tech = 8 }
			}
